data.description: Spacious 4 bedroom 2 bath house with 3 car garage and utility room. Once you walk in the foyer separate door to the upstairs loft with full bath and washer/dryer hookup, could possibly be a rental space. In walking distance to downtown Rogersville and only 4 mins to shopping area. Nice fenced in area for your pets. Come check this out!
